  USER-VISIBLE CHANGES
    1. Revised vignettes.
    2. Improved default handling of reproductive ratio and fecundity ratio.

  BUG FIXES
    1. Fixed calculation of observed lifespan in functions verticalize3() 
       and historicalize3().


CHANGES IN VERSION 2.2.1 (2020-07-18)
